net.rom.utility.system.property

Class SystemProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.rom.utility.system.property.SystemProperties

  • public final class SystemProperties
extends Object
    Contains SystemProperty fields that represent all known universal system properties on JRE 8 and newer.

      • tempDirectory

        public static final PathProperty tempDirectory
        The "java.io.tmpdir" system property.
        When SystemProperty.get() is called on this system property, the directory that its value references is created if it does not exist.
        This system property is editable.
